text: Martin Junas (born 9 March 1996) is a Slovak footballer who currently plays for Skalica as a goalkeeper. ==Club career== ===FK Senica=== Junas made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for Senica on 30 May 2015 against ŽP Šport Podbrezová.SENICA VS.
